## Project Structure

``` text
semantic-rag-engine/
  src/                  # This is where the main src code lies for rag_engine
    rag_engine/
      config.py
      loaders.py
      chunking.py
      embeddings.py
      vector_store.py
      retriever.py
      generator.py
      pipeline.py
  data/                 # All the data will reside here, raw and processed both
    raw/
    processed/
  scripts/              # Additional helper scripts that will help in ingesting and asking questions via prompt.
    ingest.py
    ask.py
  tests/                # Tests - important, well when are they not important?
```

## Tech Stack Used

- Languages: Python
- Packaging: pyproject.toml
- Testing: pytest
- Formatting and Linting: ruff
- Embeddings: sentence-formatters
- Vector Search: FAISS
- API: FastAPI
